data.description: Back on Market, no fault of Home! Showings begin on Sunday the 14th.  Come see this 2021 Bloomfield built Home. Gather around the deluxe kitchen with ss appliances, gas range, & upgraded granite countertops with an island perfect for entertaining that flows into the living room full of windows! Luxurious primary suite - sitting area, enlarged shower with upgraded tile. Split secondary bedrooms, dedicated office. Laminate wood floors downstairs. Upstairs bedroom with full bath & game room. Union Park has so much to offer! Dog park, catch-and-release pond, event pavilion, 2 rec centers, two pools, splash pad, food truck park, & MORE! HOA includes front yard maintenance.
